🧙‍♂️ My Personal Portfolio — [Your Name]
A visually rich, anime-inspired portfolio showcasing my skills, projects, and personality. Built with Next.js, styled with Tailwind CSS, and hosted on Vercel.


🌟 Features
🎨 Aesthetic background with anime-styled artwork

🧑‍🎨 Personal branding section

🔗 Social media links (GitHub, Instagram, etc.)

💻 Responsive and mobile-friendly layout

🌙 Light/Dark mode toggle (optional)

⚡ Hosted on Vercel

📦 Tech Stack
Frontend: Next.js (React)

Styling: Tailwind CSS / Framer Motion (for animations)

Icons: Heroicons, Lucide, or FontAwesome

Hosting: Vercel